subject: p15938635
History: Right clavicle and multiple rib fractures, to assess for lung expansion.
Findings: Allowing for the AP projection, there is good expansion of the right lung with no evidence of acute pneumonia or pneumothorax. Fracture of the mid shaft of the right clavicle with overriding of the fragments and several rib fractures on the right are seen.
